Package org.jscsi.target.scsi.sense.information

This package contains classes representing the content of sense data INFORMATION fields.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
EightByteInformation Information with a field length of 8 bytes.
FourByteInformation Information with a field length of 4 bytes.
Information The contents of the INFORMATION field are device-type or command specific and are defined in a command standard.
 

Package org.jscsi.target.scsi.sense.information Description

This package contains classes representing the content of sense data INFORMATION fields.
Since the jSCSI Target offers only basic error description as described in the pertinent command standards, instances of these classes currently only serve as filler, without any actual information.
